      { type: "p", text: "The Diagnosis:\nIf your score on The Switching Cost Barrier is below a 7, you are in immense danger. You do not have a strategy; you have a temporary purchase order. You are living on borrowed time until a cheaper competitor finds your buyer.\n\nYou must stop obsessing over lowering your prices, and start obsessing over increasing your buyer's switching costs." }
